<% const bttsDays = [{key:'jana', label:'Jana'}, {key:'leo', label:'Leo'}, {key:'kesho', label:'Kesho'}]; %>
<div class="section-stack">
  <section class="section-card">
    <div class="section-header">
      <div>
        <h1 class="section-title display-6 fw-bold mb-2">BTTS Tips (GG/NG)</h1>
        <p class="section-subtitle mb-0">Teams zote kufunga au la</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="lead">
      BTTS (GG/NG) ni market maarufu kwa bettors wa Kenya. Pata tips za leo na kesho kwa BTTS na ongeza chances zako za
      kuingia green.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <div class="tip-panel section-card" data-tip-category="btts">
      <div
        class="section-header flex-column flex-md-row align-items-start align-items-md-center justify-content-between gap-3 mb-3">
        <div>
          <h2 class="section-title h4 mb-1">Utabiri wa Leo - BTTS</h2>
          <p class="section-subtitle mb-0">Chagua siku kuona tips zote za GG/NG</p>
        </div>
        <ul class="nav nav-pills day-toggle" role="tablist">
          <% bttsDays.forEach(({key, label}) => { %>
          <li class="nav-item" role="presentation">
            <button class="nav-link text-dark <%= key === 'leo' ? 'active' : '' %>" id="tab-btts-<%= key %>-tab"
              data-bs-toggle="pill" data-bs-target="#tab-btts-<%= key %>" type="button" role="tab"
              aria-controls="tab-btts-<%= key %>" aria-selected="<%= key === 'leo' ? 'true' : 'false' %>">
              <%= label %>
            </button>
          </li>
          <% }) %>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="tab-content">
        <% bttsDays.forEach(({ key }) => { %>
        <div class="tab-pane fade <%= key === 'leo' ? 'show active' : '' %>" id="tab-btts-<%= key %>" role="tabpanel"
          aria-labelledby="tab-btts-<%= key %>-tab">
          <%- include('../partials/btts-cards', { tips: tips[key] || [] }) %>
        </div>
        <% }) %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-card">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2 class="section-title h4 mb-0">Mwongozo wa BTTS (GG/NG)</h2>
    </div>

    <p><b>Both Teams To Score (BTTS)</b> maarufu kama <b>GG/NG</b> ni market rahisi kuelewa. Unachotazama ni kama teams
      zote mbili zitafunga au la ndani ya dakika 90.</p>

    <p>GG (Yes) ina maana teams zote mbili zinatakiwa kufunga angalau bao moja kila moja. NG (No) ina maana mechi
      inaweza kuisha clean sheet upande mmoja au 0-0.</p>

    <h3 class="section-title h5 mb-1">Jinsi BTTS Inavyofanya Kazi (GG/NG)</h3>

    <p>BTTS inalenga uwezekano wa teams zote mbili kupata mabao. Haijalishi mechi ni ngumu au rahisi, muhimu ni teams
      zote kutikisa nyavu kabla ya final whistle.</p>

    <p>Swali kuu kabla ya kuchagua GG/NG ni: <b>Hizi teams zimekutana mara ngapi na matokeo yao yamekuwa gani?</b>
      Majibu yake yanatoka kwenye stats za head-to-head, form ya timu na strength ya ligi.</p>

    <h3 class="section-title h5 mb-1">Jinsi ya Kuchagua Mechi Sahihi za GG</h3>

    <p>Ni smart kuchagua mechi zenye chances kubwa ya teams zote kufunga, mfano:</p>

    <ul>
      <li>Teams zote zina average nzuri ya kufunga kwenye mechi 5â€“10 zilizopita</li>
      <li>Defenses za teams zote mbili ziko shaky</li>
      <li>Head-to-head inaonyesha mechi zao mara nyingi zina magoli pande zote</li>
      <li>Teams zote ni attacking na strikers wako in form</li>
    </ul>

    <p>Ni vizuri pia kuchagua mechi ambapo angalau team moja ina goal rate ya juu... hii inapunguza risk ya 0-0.</p>

    <h3 class="section-title h5 mb-1">Mifano ya Matokeo ya GG (Yes)</h3>

    <ul>
      <li>1-1</li>
      <li>2-1, 1-2</li>
      <li>2-2</li>
      <li>3-1, 1-3</li>
      <li>3-2, 2-3</li>
      <li>N.k</li>
    </ul>

    <h3 class="section-title h5 mb-1">Mifano ya Matokeo ya NG (No)</h3>

    <ul>
      <li>0-0</li>
      <li>1-0, 0-1</li>
      <li>2-0, 0-2</li>
      <li>3-0, 0-3</li>
      <li>4-0, 0-4</li>
      <li>N.k</li>
    </ul>

    <p>Kwa kifupi: GG ni nzuri kwa mechi za attacking, NG ni bora kwa mechi zenye defense imara. Tumia stats sahihi
      kuongeza chances zako.</p>
  </section>

</div>
